{"title":"抬头收获缘于低头耕耘","uid":"773280f6fbddc4d2c54f894719974634","slug":"缘苑园第61期","date":"2022-05-30T05:34:56.000Z","updated":"2022-05-30T05:44:34.972Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/缘苑园第61期.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://img1.baidu.com/it/u=2902780027,1255492734&fm=253&fmt=auto&app=138&f=JPEG?w=510&h=419","content":"<h1 id=\"缘苑园\"><a href=\"#缘苑园\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"缘苑园\"></a>缘苑园</h1><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>2022年春季刊 总第61期</p></blockquote>\n<p>​    一次在餐厅吃饭偶然看到柜台上有几本书刊，心想最近事情繁杂索性借一本来坐在店里看看以此让心静下来，告之这是结缘的佛刊。心里顿时泛起一阵涟漪，记得上次阅读佛学经典还是3年前在高阳金陵寺求来的《地藏菩萨本愿经》，这次遇到不免是其中的缘由缘分，故向餐厅工作人员借两本阅读，看到背面有郑州观音寺微信联系方式，添加后求缘最新期刊，今日已收到法宝，谢谢师傅邮寄，祝福法喜。</p>\n<p>​    很早就想在一个饭后的午间，坐在工位前阅读，听耳机里颂唱的心经，听着耳机里颂唱的心经，一上午的忙碌都泡在了茶水里，安安静静的，洗去烦恼和忧虑，我承认我的烦恼很重，当然也不完美，把静静地阅读当作自己的修行吧。那些无关紧要的言语，也与我无关。人活着就是修行，会遇到各种各样的人，各种各样的事，这些都是修行的资粮，困难跨过去了就是一次提升，感恩所有，也感恩遇见，感恩你我的相逢然后天涯。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/e6c9d24ely1h2qch7inymj21hc0o0ted.jpg\" alt=\"image-20220530130138510\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/e6c9d24ely1h2qch8g3i4j21hc0o0dls.jpg\" alt=\"image-20220530130144096\"></p>\n","text":"缘苑园 2022年春季刊 总第61期 ​ 一次在餐厅吃饭偶然看到柜台上有几本书刊，心想最近事情繁杂索性借一本来坐在店里看看以此让心静下来，告之这是结缘的佛刊。心里顿时泛起一阵涟漪，记得上次阅读佛学经典还是3年前在高阳金陵寺求来的《地藏菩萨本愿经》，这次遇到不免是其中的缘由缘分，故...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":409,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"佛缘","slug":"佛缘","count":1,"path":"api/categories/佛缘.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"缘苑园","slug":"缘苑园","count":1,"path":"api/tags/缘苑园.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%BC%98%E8%8B%91%E5%9B%AD\"><span class=\"toc-text\">缘苑园</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"zhiQiang","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"有情有颜有才缺钱","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Viserion-nlper","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"https://weibo.com/u/3902487977","zhihu":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/shuo-hao-jin-ye-bu-dian-yan","csdn":"https://blog.csdn.net/dianyanxia","juejin":"https://juejin.cn/user/40030691671550","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"/img/touxiang.jpg","link":"https://live.bilibili.com/21919321"},"baidu":{"icon":"iconfont icon-baidu","link":"https://live.bilibili.com/21919321"},"facebo